.TH ADGMix 1 local
.SH NAME
.B adgmix 
\- Graphically control soundcard mixer channels
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.ll +8
.B adgmix 
.ll -8
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.PP
.I adgmix
is a tool that lets you set the levels of your soundcard mixer channels
.PP
With adgmix you can control any
.B OSS
suported sound card mixer, there are no command line options and no console
based main program so you will need a working X11 display to use it, this
could change in future releases but by now, that's just the way it is
.PP
Thats all by now, stay in tune for other stable releases.
.PP
